readable.content: A black dog and a brown dog are jumping up to catch a red toy . A black dog and a brown dog play with a red toy on a courtyard . A brown and black lab are outside and the black lab is catching a toy in its mouth . Black dog snaps at red and black object as brown dog lunges . The Chocolate Lab jumps too late to get the toy as the Black Lab captures it in the driveway .
